---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Small Kitchen Appliance Manufacturer FAQ for B2B Buyers"
  description="FAQ for B2B buyers sourcing electric kettles, rice cookers, pressure cookers and portable lunch boxes from a China OEM and ODM manufacturer."
>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Small Kitchen Appliance Sourcing FAQ</h1>
    <p>
      Practical answers for procurement managers sourcing electric kettles,
      rice cookers, pressure cookers and portable lunch boxes from a China OEM
      and ODM appliance factory.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ SECTION -->
<section class="faq">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- NAV -->
    <div class="faq-nav">
      <a href="#general">General</a>
      <a href="#oem">OEM / ODM</a>
      <a href="#quality">Quality</a>
      <a href="#production">Production</a>
      <a href="#shipping">Shipping</a>
    </div>

    <!-- GENERAL -->
    <h2 id="general">Factory and Product Questions</h2>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Are you a factory or trading company?</summary>
      <p>
        We are a China small kitchen appliance manufacturer established in 2015.
        Our factory produces electric kettles, rice cookers, pressure cookers
        and portable lunch boxes for B2B buyers, importers and private label brands.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Where is your factory located?</summary>
      <p>
        Our production base is located in Guangdong, China. We support appliance
        production with in-house metal stamping, injection molding, assembly and
        quality inspection capabilities.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What products do you produce?</summary>
      <p>
        Our main product categories are electric kettles, rice cookers, pressure
        cookers and portable lunch boxes. These product lines are suitable for
        distributors, retailers, online sellers and brand owners.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- OEM -->
    <h2 id="oem">OEM, ODM and Private Label Questions</h2>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do you offer OEM and ODM services for B2B appliance buyers?</summary>
      <p>
        Yes. We provide OEM and ODM services for electric kettles, rice cookers,
        pressure cookers and portable lunch boxes, including logo printing,
        color customization, product specification adjustment and packaging support.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can you support private label orders?</summary>
      <p>
        Yes. We support private label orders with logo, color, packaging and
        carton customization. This is suitable for importers, regional distributors,
        supermarket buyers and e-commerce appliance brands.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can you adjust products for different target markets?</summary>
      <p>
        Yes. Our team can review your target market, plug standard, packaging
        requirements, capacity needs and compliance documents, then recommend
        suitable product specifications for your purchasing plan.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- QUALITY -->
    <h2 id="quality">Quality Control & Certifications</h2>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What certifications can support B2B import requirements?</summary>
      <p>
        Depending on the product model and target market, our products can support
        CE, RoHS and LFGB requirements. Please confirm the market and model so
        our team can advise the available documents.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How do you ensure product quality?</summary>
      <p>
        We have an independent QC team that checks raw materials, production
        process, assembly, function, appearance and final packaging before shipment.
        Inspection requirements can be aligned with buyer standards.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do you provide test reports?</summary>
      <p>
        Yes. We can provide available test reports, certification documents and
        factory information based on the product model and customer requirements.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- PRODUCTION -->
    <h2 id="production">Production & MOQ</h2>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What is your MOQ for OEM and private label orders?</summary>
      <p>
        Our standard MOQ is usually 1,000 units per model. MOQ may vary by product
        category, customization level, packaging requirements and current production schedule.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How long is the production lead time?</summary>
      <p>
        Standard production lead time is usually 30-45 days after sample approval,
        packaging confirmation and deposit receipt. Exact timing depends on the
        model, order quantity and customization details.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can I request samples before order?</summary>
      <p>
        Yes. Samples are available for quality review, market evaluation and
        internal approval before mass production. Custom samples can be arranged
        after specifications are confirmed.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- SHIPPING -->
    <h2 id="shipping">Shipping & Export</h2>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Which countries do you export to?</summary>
      <p>
        We support buyers from Europe, the Middle East, Southeast Asia and other
        global markets that source small kitchen appliances from China.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What shipping terms do you support?</summary>
      <p>
        We can support EXW, FOB, CIF and other international trade terms based on
        buyer requirements, destination port and logistics arrangement.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What information should I send for a quotation?</summary>
      <p>
        Please send the product category, target quantity, market, plug type,
        logo and packaging needs, certification requirements and expected delivery
        schedule. Our team usually replies within 24 hours.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="cta">
      <h2>Need a Supplier Quote for Your Purchasing Plan?</h2>
      <p>
        Talk to our OEM and ODM team about electric kettles, rice cookers,
        pressure cookers or portable lunch boxes for your next B2B sourcing project.
      </p>

      <a href="https://www.yolec-electronics.com/contact/" class="btn">
        Request OEM Quote
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<!-- STYLE -->
<style>

.hero{
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
  padding:110px 20px;
  text-align:center;
  background:
    linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.52), rgba(0,0,0,0.52)),
    url("/images/yolec-electric.png") center/cover no-repeat;
}

.hero h1{
  font-size:42px;
  margin-bottom:12px;
  color:#fff;
}

.hero p{
  max-width:800px;
  margin:auto;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  line-height:1.6;
}

.faq{
  padding:60px 20px 100px;
}

.container{
  max-width:1100px;
  margin:auto;
}

.faq-nav{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  gap:10px;
  margin-bottom:50px;
}

.faq-nav a{
  padding:8px 14px;
  border:1px solid #e5e5e5;
  border-radius:30px;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-size:14px;
  color:#333;
  transition:0.3s;
}

.faq-nav a:hover{
  background:#111;
  color:#fff;
}

h2{
  font-size:24px;
  margin:45px 0 20px;
  text-align:left;
}

.faq-item{
  background:#fff;
  border:1px solid #eee;
  border-radius:12px;
  padding:16px 18px;
  margin-bottom:12px;
  transition:0.3s;
}

.faq-item:hover{
  box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
}

summary{
  cursor:pointer;
  font-weight:600;
  font-size:16px;
  list-style:none;
}

summary::-webkit-details-marker{
  display:none;
}

.faq-item p{
  margin-top:10px;
  color:#555;
  line-height:1.6;
  font-size:14px;
}

.cta{
  margin-top:70px;
  padding:50px 30px;
  text-align:center;
  background:#f5f6f8;
  border-radius:16px;
}

.cta h2{
  text-align:center;
  margin-bottom:10px;
}

.cta p{
  max-width:700px;
  margin:0 auto 20px;
  color:#555;
}

.btn{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:12px 22px;
  background:#ff6600;
  color:#fff;
  text-decoration:none;
  border-radius:6px;
  font-weight:600;
}

@media (max-width:768px){
  .hero{padding:90px 20px;}
  .hero h1{font-size:32px;}
  h2{font-size:20px;}
}

</style>
